  "root_text": {
    "iti65:0.1": "Itivuttaka 65 ",
    "iti65:0.2": "Tikanipāta ",
    "iti65:0.3": "Dutiyavagga ",
    "iti65:0.4": "Sucaritasutta ",
    "iti65:1.1": "Vuttañhetaṁ bhagavatā vuttamarahatāti me sutaṁ: ",
    "iti65:2.1": "“Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, sucaritāni. ",
    "iti65:2.2": "Katamāni tīṇi? ",
    "iti65:2.3": "Kāyasucaritaṁ, vacīsucaritaṁ, manosucaritaṁ—",
    "iti65:2.4": "imāni kho, bhikkhave, tīṇi sucaritānī”ti. ",
    "iti65:2.5": "Etamatthaṁ bhagavā avoca. ",
    "iti65:2.6": "Tatthetaṁ iti vuccati: ",
    "iti65:3.1": "“Kāyaduccaritaṁ hitvā, ",
    "iti65:3.2": "vacīduccaritāni ca; ",
    "iti65:3.3": "Manoduccaritaṁ hitvā, ",
    "iti65:3.4": "yañcaññaṁ dosasaṁhitaṁ. ",
    "iti65:4.1": "Akatvākusalaṁ kammaṁ, ",
    "iti65:4.2": "katvāna kusalaṁ bahuṁ; ",
    "iti65:4.3": "Kāyassa bhedā sappañño, ",
    "iti65:4.4": "saggaṁ so upapajjatī”ti. ",
    "iti65:5.1": "Ayampi attho vutto bhagavatā, iti me sutanti. ",
    "iti65:5.2": "Chaṭṭhaṁ. "
  },
  "translation_text": {
    "iti65:0.1": "So It Was Said 65 ",
    "iti65:0.2": "The Book of the Threes ",
    "iti65:0.3": "Chapter Two ",
    "iti65:0.4": "Good Conduct ",
    "iti65:1.1": "This was said by the Buddha, the Perfected One: that is what I heard. ",
    "iti65:2.1": "“Mendicants, there are these kinds of good conduct. ",
    "iti65:2.2": "What three? ",
    "iti65:2.3": "Good conduct by way of body, speech, and mind. ",
    "iti65:2.4": "These are the three kinds of good conduct.” ",
    "iti65:2.5": "The Buddha spoke this matter. ",
    "iti65:2.6": "On this it is said: ",
    "iti65:3.1": "“Having given up bad conduct ",
    "iti65:3.2": "by way of body, ",
    "iti65:3.3": "speech, and mind, ",
    "iti65:3.4": "and whatever else is corrupt; ",
    "iti65:4.1": "not having done bad deeds, ",
    "iti65:4.2": "and having done many good, ",
    "iti65:4.3": "when their body breaks up, that wise person ",
    "iti65:4.4": "is reborn in heaven.” ",
    "iti65:5.1": "This too is a matter that was spoken by the Blessed One: that is what I heard. "
  },
